{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were very liberal, the Dutch, but during the war, they forgot about that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there were some very fine people who at very great risk to themselves hid people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's-- it's a very complicated thing to hide somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not only do you have them living in your house, you have to supply them with food and food was rationed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And once you're not-- you don't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You didn't get a ration card, so they had to buy the food on the black market, which was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, it was very dangerous too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now if you had one or two people hiding, that mean you had to feed one or two people more.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you had to have money, too, for that also, to be able to sustain.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because most of these families didn't have-- were not wealthy enough that they could hide you and--and also support you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And of course, the risk was that if you were caught, you-- not only were you done for but the family who hid you were also shot or taken to camps.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it was a very dangerous and very brave thing to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And according to the statistics, of-- about 20,000 Jews were hiding at one time or another in Holland out of 140,000, which is a relatively small percentage, but still 20,000 or so, that means 20,000 families or whatever.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The unfortunate thing is 8,000 of those were betrayed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's almost 40%.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who betrayed them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fellow Dutch.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't the Germans who found them, it was somebody who went to the Germans and said, hey, I think there are some Jews living at Mr.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-and-so's or my neighbors or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't trust your neighbors.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
